description.narrative: This award strives to help foreign partners professionalize their military forces through educational programs and technical support, ensuring that their force can develop and maintain the requisite capacity to effectively carry out its military mission through reliance on discipline, accountability, effective professional standards, and technical expertise. More specifically, this includes Jignasa (Jenny) Parikh, COR[Covers services supplied by other U.S. Government agencies not otherwise classified.]. Covers services supplied by other U.S. Government agencies not otherwise classified.. SUPPLY/TRANSP/PROCUREMENT Jignasa (Jenny) Parikh, COR[Covers services supplied by other U.S. Government agencies not otherwise classified.]. Jignasa (Jenny) Parikh, COR[Management and professional support services generally aim at improving the efficiency or effectiveness of management or administrative systems and normally take the form of information, opinion, advice, training or direct assistance. Contracts may be with firms or individuals.]. SUPPLY/TRANSP/PROCUREMENT[Covers services supplied by other U.S. Government agencies not otherwise classified.]. Information Redacted , COR[Covers services supplied by other U.S. Government agencies not otherwise classified.].

Through educational programs and technical support, help foreign partners professionalize their military forces, ensuring that their force can develop and maintain the requisite capacity to effectively carry out its military mission through reliance on discipline, accountability, effective professional standards, and technical expertise. In addition, activities assist foreign partners so that their military forces reliably demonstrate consistent support for adherence to norms of human rights; support the concept of civilian executive authority/control of the military; and have the capacity for institutional and security sector reform.
